canonical:
  title: 謝宣賜生日起居表
  author: 金富儀
  language: lzh
  text: 守封域於海濱第勤述職望宸居於天上愈切懸心
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 謝宣賜生日起居表
  author: 金富儀
  language: lzh
  text: 守封域於海濱。第勤述職。望宸居於天上。愈切懸心。
korean:
  title: 사선사생일기거표
  author: 김부의
  language: kor
  text: 바닷가에 봉역(封域)을 지켜 다만 조공의 구실을 부지런히 하오며, 하늘 위에 신거(宸居)를 바라보면서 더욱 연궐(戀闕)의 마음을 간절히 가지옵나이다.
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0380_010_0140&viewSync=OT
english:
  title: A Memorial of Gratitude for the King's Birthday Regards
  author: Kim Bu-ui
  language: eng
  text: Guarding the realm at the edge of the sea, I diligently fulfill my duties as a subject. Gazing toward the celestial residence above, my longing for the court grows ever more fervent.
  footnotes:
    - The 'realm at the edge of the sea' refers to Kim Bu-ui's provincial posting, emphasizing his distance from the capital.
    - The 'celestial residence' (宸居) is a poetic reference to the royal court, suggesting the spiritual and political center of the kingdom.
